Maintainer: Jacopo Beghetto <jacopo.beghetto@unil.ch>
Description: The package will recall a shiny app regarding "Performance Scoreboard 
             for Recruitment".
             The app was built by group E and by inserting the result of some 
             phisical exercises, will give you a possible weapon class of belonging.
             The app is entirely in English with video in French regarding the 
             exercises to do. 
             The app contains also two main function essential for our purpose.
             The first one return the graph and will create a list of points.
             The second one is correlated to the first one as it will create a
             data-frame listing weapons class based on the sum of point from the 
             list created before.
